Development:
```bash
pnpm dev
pnpm start
```

Build:
```bash
pnpm build
```

Code quality:
```bash
pnpm lint
pnpm lint:fix
pnpm format
```

Database:
```bash
pnpm db:generate
pnpm db:migrate
pnpm db:studio
pnpm db:push
```

Testing:
```bash
pnpm test
```
